high_descs: Turn around and walk to the cabinet to the left of the fireplace.
Pick up the award on the cabinet.
Turn around and walk forward and then right, and go to the far right corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: View a trophy by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn right, head towards the dresser, then turn right and walk towards the trophy on other side of the room.
Pick up the trophy from the table.
Turn around and walk towards the entrance of the room on the right, enter the room, walk straight to the black dresser, turn right towards the pink lamp.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a trophy by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn right, walk forward to the dresser, then turn right and walk to the statue on the small end table.
Pick up the statue from the end table.
Turn around, walk forward and then turn right into the other room, then walk to the floor lamp in the upper right corner of the room.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the light of a floor lamp.

high_descs: Move across the room to the small black table where the window is
Pick up the gold statue on top of the black table
Carry the gold statue over to the large floor lamp along the yellow wall
Turn on the lamp
anns.task_desc: Turn on a lamp while holding a statue

high_descs: Turn right and move towards the black dresser and then turn right again and move towards and face the small table in front of the window.
Pick up the small golden trophy on the table.
Turn left and move towards the small cabinet next to the stool and then turn right and move and face the lamp in the corner of the room.
Turn on the floor lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a trophy by the light of a floor lamp.
